{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1000,"text":"Let me introduce to you Rezero."},{"time":4000,"text":"This little fellow was developed"},{"time":6000,"text":"by a group of 10 undergraduate students"},{"time":8000,"text":"at the Autonomous Systems Laboratory"},{"time":10000,"text":"at ETH-Zurich."}]},{"cues":[{"time":12000,"text":"Our robot belongs to a family of robots"},{"time":14000,"text":"called Ballbots."},{"time":16000,"text":"Instead of wheels, a Ballbot is balancing"},{"time":18000,"text":"and moving on one single ball."},{"time":20000,"text":"The main characteristics of such a system is"},{"time":22000,"text":"that there's one sole contact point to the ground."},{"time":25000,"text":"This means that the robot"},{"time":27000,"text":"is inherently unstable."},{"time":29000,"text":"It's like when I am trying to stand"},{"time":31000,"text":"on one foot."}]},{"cues":[{"time":32000,"text":"You might ask yourself, what's the usefulness"},{"time":34000,"text":"of a robot that's unstable?"},{"time":36000,"text":"Now we'll explain that in a second."},{"time":38000,"text":"Let me first explain how Rezero"},{"time":40000,"text":"actually keeps his balance."},{"time":42000,"text":"Rezero keeps his balance by constantly"},{"time":44000,"text":"measuring his pitch angle with a sensor."},{"time":47000,"text":"He then counteracts and avoids toppling over"},{"time":50000,"text":"by turning the motors appropriately."},{"time":52000,"text":"This happens 160 times per second,"},{"time":54000,"text":"and if anything fails in this process,"},{"time":56000,"text":"Rezero would immediately fall to the ground."}]},{"cues":[{"time":59000,"text":"Now to move and to balance,"},{"time":61000,"text":"Rezero needs to turn the ball."},{"time":63000,"text":"The ball is driven by three special wheels"},{"time":65000,"text":"that allow Rezero to move into any direction"},{"time":68000,"text":"and also move around his own axis"},{"time":70000,"text":"at the same time."},{"time":74000,"text":"Due to his instability, Rezero is always"},{"time":76000,"text":"in motion. Now here's the trick."},{"time":78000,"text":"It's indeed exactly this instability that allows"},{"time":81000,"text":"a robot to move very [dynamically]."},{"time":83000,"text":"Let's play a little."},{"time":85000,"text":"You may have wondered what happens"},{"time":87000,"text":"if I give the robot a little push."},{"time":92000,"text":"In this mode, he's trying to maintain"},{"time":94000,"text":"his position."}]},{"cues":[{"time":97000,"text":"For the next demo, I'd like you to introduce"},{"time":100000,"text":"to my colleagues Michael, on the computer,"},{"time":103000,"text":"and Thomas who's helping me onstage."},{"time":107000,"text":"In the next mode, Rezero is passive,"},{"time":109000,"text":"and we can move him around."},{"time":113000,"text":"With almost no force I can control"},{"time":115000,"text":"his position and his velocity."},{"time":121000,"text":"I can also make him spin."},{"time":135000,"text":"In the next mode, we can get Rezero"},{"time":137000,"text":"to follow a person."},{"time":140000,"text":"He's now keeping a constant distance to Thomas."},{"time":147000,"text":"This works with a laser sensor"},{"time":149000,"text":"that's mounted on top of Rezero."},{"time":155000,"text":"With the same method, we can also"},{"time":157000,"text":"get him to circle a person."},{"time":162000,"text":"We call this the orbiting mode."},{"time":175000,"text":"All right, thank you, Thomas."},{"time":177000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":181000,"text":"Now, what's the use of this technology?"},{"time":187000,"text":"For now, it's an experiment, but let me"},{"time":189000,"text":"show you some possible future applications."},{"time":193000,"text":"Rezero could be used in exhibitions or parks."},{"time":195000,"text":"With a screen it could inform people or show"},{"time":197000,"text":"them around in a fun and entertaining way."},{"time":200000,"text":"In a hospital, this device could be used to"},{"time":202000,"text":"carry around medical equipment."},{"time":204000,"text":"Due to the Ballbot system, it has a very small"},{"time":206000,"text":"footprint and it's also easy to move around."},{"time":209000,"text":"And of course, who wouldn't like"},{"time":211000,"text":"to take a ride on one of these."},{"time":214000,"text":"And these are more practical applications."},{"time":216000,"text":"But there's also a certain beauty"},{"time":218000,"text":"within this technology."}]},{"cues":[{"time":220000,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":283000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":284000,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":286000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":290000,"text":"Thank you."}]}]}